# Build artifacts — every lineage builds its CLI into <lineage>/bin/.
# Patterns are anchored to lineage roots on purpose: an unanchored "bin/"
# would also swallow real source dirs like rust/src/bin/.
/*/bin/
/*/build/
/*/target/
/*/dist-newstyle/
/*/_build/
/*/.dub/
*.o
*.a
conformance/__pycache__/
